  "raw_sections": [
    "Thepath oftherighteous",
    "islike thelight ofdawn,",
    "whichshines brighterandbrighter",
    "until thefullday.",
    "Then therighteous",
    "willshine forthlike thesun",
    "in thekingdomof theirFather.",
    "Lord, weloveYouand Yourappearing!",
    "Make usthose whobring Youback.",
    "Lord, increase inusfor Yourcoming",
    "'Til themorningstarrisesin ourhearts.",
    "And thosewhohave",
    "insightwillshine like",
    "the shiningof theheavenly expanse,",
    "and thosewhoturn",
    "manytorighteousness,",
    "like thestars, foreverand ever.",
    "Lord, weloveYouand Yourappearing!",
